of the same spells at an even higher level that cost<br>
a component for somewhere we could just portal<br>
to anyway. I'll admit Cazic translocation is very<br>
useful since I wouldn't touch the port or self gate<br>
with a 10 foot staff of the four but my god I hope<br>
they like renovate the combine place in Dreadlands<br>
and like rape the tomes of all the ancient wizard<br>
spells so we can get to exping and such. I know<br>
they keep saying we aren't about buffs or other<br>
stuff like that but transportation and nuking is 2<br>
things that we don't really do well enough to be<br>
called our only specialties. Well, snaring too but<br>
to a lesser point. I know I had a point when I<br>
started typing here but I seem to have forgotten<br>
it so here's to hoping they get a brilliant idea<br>
to fix wizards once and for all in the next few days.<br>
